address2: Unit 5–6 23rd Floor 39 Wang Chiu Road Kowloon Bay
longBusinessSummary: IPE Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells precision metal components and assembled parts for use in automotive parts, hydraulic equipment, and electronic equipment component and other devices in Thailand, Malaysia, Mainland China, Macau, Hong Kong, North America, Europe, and internationally. The company also provides surface and deburring treatment services, as well as manufactures and trades in intelligent equipment. It serves information technology, fluid power, automotive, and electronic sectors. IPE Group Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. IPE Group Limited is a subsidiary of Baoan Technology Company Limited.
